t very small- I climbed the one level with the base of the Comb</div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-6K-N3RZgVtw/WEHIlQkeI7I/AAAAAAAAX1g/eLzZKL53rB4vNY6DegWydSVJOVWVc6CwACLcB/s1600/P1000715.JPG" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="320" src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-6K-N3RZgVtw/WEHIlQkeI7I/AAAAAAAAX1g/eLzZKL53rB4vNY6DegWydSVJOVWVc6CwACLcB/s320/P1000715.JPG" width="240" /></a></div><div style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;Here it is</div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-sWDFahLZal8/WEHIqA5iDiI/AAAAAAAAX1o/eWaxVKUzmvEcF6T2NKOBAnmETlJtY19DwCLcB/s1600/P1000718.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="320" src="https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-sWDFahLZal8/WEHIqA5iDiI/AAAAAAAAX1o/eWaxVKUzmvEcF6T2NKOBAnmETlJtY19DwCLcB/s320/P1000718.jpg" width="240" /></a></div><div style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;The 'flume' where No.2 has avalanched</div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-wQTVq2N9Ubs/WEHInq6iSOI/AAAAAAAAX1k/r2Aawh_An4Ya-VSIoftHF2kckWQtRE3eACLcB/s1600/P1000719.JPG" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="240" src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-wQTVq2N9Ubs/WEHInq6iSOI/AAAAAAAAX1k/r2Aawh_An4Ya-VSIoftHF2kckWQtRE3eACLcB/s320/P1000719.JPG" width="320" /></a></div><div style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;Looking up at Raeburns Easy and the Cascade-very patchy</div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-_Lf-OYZYqNI/WEHIvDgfw4I/AAAAAAAAX1w/Kx5jw-WyMSo4yd7ao2V4Y18Svzm9o4UswCLcB/s1600/P1000722.JPG" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="240" src="https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-_Lf-OYZYqNI/WEHIvDgfw4I/AAAAAAAAX1w/Kx5jw-WyMSo4yd7ao2V4Y18Svzm9o4UswCLcB/s320/